*PPD-Adobe: "4.3"
*FormatVersion: "4.3"
*FileVersion: "1.0"
*LanguageVersion: English
*LanguageEncoding: ISOLatin1
*PCFileName: "xprtv3.ppd"
*Manufacturer: "Xprinter"
*Product: "(Xprinter V3)"
*ModelName: "Xprinter V3 Thermal Label"
*ShortNickName: "Xprinter V3"
*NickName: "Xprinter V3 Thermal Label Printer"
*PSVersion: "(3010.000) 0"
*LanguageLevel: "3"
*ColorDevice: False
*DefaultColorSpace: Gray
*FileSystem: False
*Throughput: "1"
*LandscapeOrientation: Plus90
*TTRasterizer: Type42
*% Filter: pdftopdf scales/crops PDF to label size, then our filter converts to TSPL
*cupsFilter: "application/vnd.cups-pdf 0 xprinter-tspl"
*cupsModelNumber: 0
*cupsManualCopies: True

*% ============ Resolution ============
*OpenUI *Resolution/Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *Resolution
*DefaultResolution: 203dpi
*Resolution 203dpi/203 DPI (Standard): "<</HWResolution[203 203]>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*% ============ Label Sizes (PageSize) ============
*OpenUI *PageSize/Label Size: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 30 AnySetup *PageSize
*DefaultPageSize: w164h113

*PageSize w57h28/20 x 10 mm: "<</PageSize[57 28]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize w85h57/30 x 20 mm: "<</PageSize[85 57]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize w113h57/40 x 20 mm: "<</PageSize[113 57]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize w113h85/40 x 30 mm: "<</PageSize[113 85]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
