*PageSize w170h113/60 x 40 mm: "<</PageSize[170 113]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize w227h142/80 x 50 mm: "<</PageSize[227 142]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize w227h170/80 x 60 mm: "<</PageSize[227 170]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize w283h170/100 x 60 mm: "<</PageSize[283 170]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
