*PageRegion w113h57/40 x 20 mm: "<</PageSize[113 57]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w113h85/40 x 30 mm: "<</PageSize[113 85]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w164h85/58 x 30 mm: "<</PageSize[164 85]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w164h113/58 x 40 mm: "<</PageSize[164 113]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w170h113/60 x 40 mm: "<</PageSize[170 113]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w227h142/80 x 50 mm: "<</PageSize[227 142]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
