*PageRegion w283h425/100 x 150 mm: "<</PageSize[283 425]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w340h213/120 x 75 mm: "<</PageSize[340 213]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"

*CloseUI: *PageRegion

