*% ============ Custom Options ============
*OpenUI *XprinterDensity/Print Darkness: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50 AnySetup *XprinterDensity
*DefaultXprinterDensity: 8
*XprinterDensity 1/1 (Lightest): ""
*XprinterDensity 3/3 (Light): ""
*XprinterDensity 5/5 (Medium-Light): ""
*XprinterDensity 8/8 (Normal): ""
*XprinterDensity 10/10 (Dark): ""
*XprinterDensity 12/12 (Darker): ""
*XprinterDensity 15/15 (Darkest): ""
