*OpenUI *XprinterSpeed/Print Speed: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50 AnySetup *XprinterSpeed
*DefaultXprinterSpeed: 3
*XprinterSpeed 1/1 (Slowest): ""
*XprinterSpeed 2/2: ""
*XprinterSpeed 3/3 (Normal): ""
*XprinterSpeed 4/4: ""
*XprinterSpeed 5/5 (Fastest): ""
*CloseUI: *XprinterSpeed

*OpenUI *XprinterGap/Label Gap: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50 AnySetup *XprinterGap
*DefaultXprinterGap: 2
*XprinterGap 0/0 mm (No Gap): ""
*XprinterGap 2/2 mm (Standard): ""
*XprinterGap 3/3 mm: ""
*XprinterGap 4/4 mm: ""
